title: 'dopamine : seeking :?: serotonin : enjoying'
pid: 8017ec64-999c-43a6-8554-88345d61df82
body: |2-
  Dopamine and serotonin are both associated with positive affect, but dopamine happens when triggered by positive stimuli and seeking them, whereas serotonin is the happiness of the afterglow or something.
